Man oh man so my weekend was pretty dumb.. Well on Friday I went with Brooke to the Hockey game because, Brooke and I love going (yelling at Clintron haha just kidding). That was fun but of course FREEZING. There was a lot of people there at the hockey game this time, but we lost bad 7-1 because, Dustin one of the best players on the team his ice skates were broken or something I don't remember. Then after wards we went to Sonic (of course fatties represent ha ha). Then we went home for a bit and then went to Travis's house and met Will. He was pretty cool. On Saturday it was K's Birthday (HE'S A MAN MUAHAHA) and it was just crazy I hated it! I got drunk and embarrassed myself in front of EVERYONE. But I don't feel like putting the details. On Sunday was K's birthday party but I didn't go cause I didn't feel to good (if ya know what I mean). So I felt really bad but I would've just made a fool out of myself anyways ha ha. And today I'm going to go to the Texas Baptist Church and give gifts to the children. Its going to be funnnn.

Well I hope everyone has a good turkey day.

I was super excited when I found out I made it but I didn't want to upset everyone and get excited in front of them. I'm about to go to a Pep- Rally so I'm super excited! WOO ha ha. but I'll tty everyone after this weekend! have a good weekend guys.
